title: Smiling Face
body: A yellow face with a heart-shaped mouth, eyes closed, and red hearts for pupils.

title: Angry Face
body: A red face with a frowning mouth and furrowed eyebrows, with anger or annoyance.

title: Crying Face
body: A yellow face with raised eyebrows and a slight frown, shedding a tear from one eye down its cheek.

title: Heart Eyes
body: A yellow face with a heart-shaped mouth, eyes closed, and red hearts for pupils.

title: Laughing with Tears
body: A yellow face with a big grin, raised eyebrows, and smiling eyes, with tears streaming down both cheeks from laughing too hard.

title: Winking Face
body: A yellow face with a slight smile and a winking eye, used to convey flirtation or joking.

title: Thinking Face
body: A yellow face with furrowed eyebrows looking upwards with thumb and index finger resting on its chin.

title: Hugging Face
body: A yellow face smiling with open hands, as if giving a hug.
